  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Explain the origins of Earth&#8217;s ocean tides</item>
<item>Describe how neap and leap tides differ</item>
<item>Describe how tidal forces affect binary systems</item>
</list></md:abstract>
